<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-463] Add feature documentation for Erasure Coding</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-463</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add feature documentation for erasure coding, added in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10911&quot; title=&quot;FLR2: Read only erasure coding &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10911&quot;&gt;LU-10911&lt;/a&gt;. This should include in-tree documentation that describes the overall EC component layout (Ronnie&apos;s &lt;tt&gt;Documentation/ec.txt&lt;/tt&gt; to ensure it is uptodate), updates to the Lustre Operations manual (see &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.lustre.org/Lustre_Manual_Changes&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Lustre Manual Changes&lt;/a&gt;), as well as any changes to &lt;tt&gt;lfs mirror&lt;/tt&gt; sub-commands in &lt;tt&gt;Documentation/man1&lt;/tt&gt; and parameter files in &lt;tt&gt;Documentation/man4&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is also information available in the &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.lustre.org/Erasure_Coding_Read-Only_High_Level_Design#EC_Geometry&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Lustre Erasure Coding Read-Only HLD&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
